  {title: "Orange Bacon", excerpt: "Except it is made for me!", create_date: "2017-03-06", author: "Bartender Ascelina", body: "acon ipsum dolor amet kevin jerky landjaeger jowl. Swine doner biltong, ham hock t-bone shank rump. Tenderloin rump beef sausage brisket pork ham kielbasa tongue shankle chicken pork belly jowl picanha. Alcatra chicken ground round, pork belly ball tip biltong pig andouille burgdoggen frankfurter venison beef picanha tongue turducken. Porchetta ribeye rump pork chop pastrami tenderloin bacon ham jowl pork belly turducken. Meatball kielbasa turkey fatback brisket burgdoggen shank salami sausage drumstick boudin short loin porchetta venison beef ribs.\r\n\r\nPicanha burgdoggen jowl flank pig pork kielbasa. T-bone pastrami ground round bresaola short ribs fatback ham. Landjaeger chuck biltong spare ribs tail filet mignon beef ribs strip steak shoulder shank kielbasa pork tenderloin pastrami. T-bone swine short ribs pastrami flank. Shank beef ribs chuck brisket picanha filet mignon, pork loin jerky bacon meatball chicken ham hock strip steak turkey porchetta. Flank corned beef sirloin, spare ribs strip steak sausage drumstick boudin.\r\n\r\nPork ribeye boudin salami pork loin meatloaf pancetta biltong short loin burgdoggen cow kielbasa landjaeger ground round swine. Chicken hamburger tail, kevin t-bone leberkas bresaola. Pork pork belly tongue pork chop rump. Tenderloin burgdoggen ribeye prosciutto venison.", category_id: "5", image_file_name: "orangebacon.jpg", image_content_type: "image/jpeg", image_file_size: 244685, image_updated_at: "2017-03-06 01:00:55", user_id: nil},
  {title: "Sub Bacon Drink", excerpt: "Bacon subway classic is everything", create_date: "2017-03-06", author: "Bartender Sub", body: "acon ipsum dolor amet kevin jerky landjaeger jowl. Swine doner biltong, ham hock t-bone shank rump. Tenderloin rump beef sausage brisket pork ham kielbasa tongue shankle chicken pork belly jowl picanha. Alcatra chicken ground round, pork belly ball tip biltong pig andouille burgdoggen frankfurter venison beef picanha tongue turducken. Porchetta ribeye rump pork chop pastrami tenderloin bacon ham jowl pork belly turducken. Meatball kielbasa turkey fatback brisket burgdoggen shank salami sausage drumstick boudin short loin porchetta venison beef ribs.\r\n\r\nPicanha burgdoggen jowl flank pig pork kielbasa. T-bone pastrami ground round bresaola short ribs fatback ham. Landjaeger chuck biltong spare ribs tail filet mignon beef ribs strip steak shoulder shank kielbasa pork tenderloin pastrami. T-bone swine short ribs pastrami flank. Shank beef ribs chuck brisket picanha filet mignon, pork loin jerky bacon meatball chicken ham hock strip steak turkey porchetta. Flank corned beef sirloin, spare ribs strip steak sausage drumstick boudin.\r\n\r\nPork ribeye boudin salami pork loin meatloaf pancetta biltong short loin burgdoggen cow kielbasa landjaeger ground round swine. Chicken hamburger tail, kevin t-bone leberkas bresaola. Pork pork belly tongue pork chop rump. Tenderloin burgdoggen ribeye prosciutto venison.", category_id: "5", image_file_name: "subbacon.jpg", image_content_type: "image/jpeg", image_file_size: 84945, image_updated_at: "2017-03-06 01:02:44", user_id: nil},
  {title: "Bacon is king ", excerpt: "I figured it out bitches", create_date: "2017-03-07", author: "CHef Fuck yeah", body: "Bacon ipsum dolor amet shankle shank pork chop short ribs t-bone brisket frankfurter pork pork belly tongue. Ham hock kielbasa picanha salami pastrami chuck ground round capicola flank brisket boudin beef ribs pork chop cow turducken. Doner swine turducken hamburger strip steak sirloin. Cupim bacon pork loin tail pork, beef ribs capicola short ribs landjaeger meatball. Corned beef pork bacon, jowl kevin t-bone beef ribs ribeye.\r\n\r\nFrankfurter shank brisket ball tip chicken sausage ham hock turducken pork capicola prosciutto jerky meatloaf. Tongue capicola drumstick, filet mignon cupim hamburger meatloaf. Kevin tongue shank salami flank jerky shoulder pork chop ham ribeye short ribs. Hamburger boudin burgdoggen ham beef.\r\n\r\nMeatball venison strip steak leberkas. Fatback cupim frankfurter kielbasa leberkas pork loin chuck flank drumstick alcatra boudin meatloaf short loin. Shoulder cupim sirloin, frankfurter swine corned beef capicola rump venison pork chop salami landjaeger. Shoulder frankfurter porchetta andouille salami venison. Hamburger meatloaf rump landjaeger.", category_id: "3", image_file_name: "bacon_king.jpg", image_content_type: "image/jpeg", image_file_size: 78333, image_updated_at: "2017-03-07 23:39:50", user_id: 1},
